author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the end of an MMO that I've been playing since it's inception. GTA Online has been a part of my life through many ups and downs and seeing it finally reach end of life is something I wanted to talk about for a while. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: I'm Done...
